reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 22, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars This thing is Awesome!
reviews.reviewText: I love this brush holder/cleaner. It’s a very genius, unique invention, and I’m so glad I bought it. If you’re make up person and you have a lot of brushes/beauty blenders, you will definitely get the best use out of this. I just keep my brushes standing up inside of it just as storage, which I don’t have to do, but it’s so convenient. If you use the proper slots, the brushes won’t come out when you stick them inside. So that means you can turn it upside down if you need to wash one brush, while the other brushes remain stuck inside the bottom, and they won’t fall out. Just a clever invention. I 100% recommend it. And I look forward to this company next invention. By the way, I don’t know who manufactured this product originally but, whoever did, kudos to you!

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Where have you been all my life?
reviews.reviewText: I have been searching for such a product for my beauty brushes and sponges for my art supplies. This is so awesome. The design to hold the brushes is chefs kiss. Excellent product. I put a small towel down to catch any drips. And everything is firmly put it. If you do come out with a painting version for thicker handles let me know. 10 out of 10.
